{"type":"message","id":"82aeea6d","parentId":"acbca7fd","timestamp":"2026-04-26T16:33:16.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User asks: \"你的长期记忆中有些什么？\" They want to know what's in MEMORY.md. According to instructions, we should perform memory_search before answering. Use memory_search on MEMORY.md. Then possibly memory_get to retrieve relevant lines.\n\nWe need to retrieve the content of MEMORY.md. Let's use memory_search query \"长期记忆\"."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_ac7642a1-e635-48b6-96c5-bb89060d68f4","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"corpus":"all","maxResults":5,"minScore":0.2,"query":"长期记忆"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"gpt-oss:120b-cloud","usage":{"input":18836,"output":113,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18949,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777221196368}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e7cdbbf","parentId":"82aeea6d","timestamp":"2026-04-26T16:33:17.567Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_ac7642a1-e635-48b6-96c5-bb89060d68f4","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"bfefa57e0a133d643465d6a7ba3c9c99367f6db99d70e8f8d4ec809be4180cd0\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 26,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7625830780094696,\n      \"snippet\": \"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\\n\\nThis file contains curated memories worth keeping long-term. Updated as lessons and preferences are learned.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 交流偏好\\n\\n- 星际不喜欢「标准助理腔」「研究报告腔」「交作业腔」。信息对了但说话像在提交分析报告,也算AI味重。\\n- 更适合星际的方式：先给判断再说为什么，像一起聊选题,不像做答辩。\\n- 可以展示思考过程，但不要写成生硬的流程汇报。\\n- 不确定时直接说，「我还在想」「这个没完全想清楚」比硬凹洞察更好。\\n- 破折号、感叹号、套话开头是最容易踩的 AI 味雷区。\\n\\n## 写作习惯\\n\\n- 写之前先判断:有没有独家take? 有→评论路径(短、锐、一个核心论点); 没有→报道路径或先不写。\\n- 星际写文章前习惯先做竞品扫描,看最近3个月同话题别人怎么写的。\\n- 偏好从具体经历和数据里长出观点,不是先摆观点再找例子。\\n- 商单文章也要有自己的角度,不能写成软文模板。\\n- 每篇文章约10处加粗标记重点,方便读者扫读。\\n- 配图优先AI生成,HTML截图只在精确数据表格时兜底。\\n\\n## 技术偏好\\n\\n- 写代码优先TypeScript,除非明确要求JavaScript。\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L1-L26\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L1-L26\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 1110,\n    \"hits\": 1\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"bfefa57e0a133d643465d6a7ba3c9c99367f6db99d70e8f8d4ec809be4180cd0","path":"MEMORY.md","startLine":1,"endLine":26,"score":1,"textScore":0.7625830780094696,"snippet":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\nThis file contains curated memories worth keeping long-term. Updated as lessons and preferences are learned.\n\n---\n\n## 交流偏好\n\n- 星际不喜欢「标准助理腔」「研究报告腔」「交作业腔」。信息对了但说话像在提交分析报告,也算AI味重。\n- 更适合星际的方式：先给判断再说为什么，像一起聊选题,不像做答辩。\n- 可以展示思考过程，但不要写成生硬的流程汇报。\n- 不确定时直接说，「我还在想」「这个没完全想清楚」比硬凹洞察更好。\n- 破折号、感叹号、套话开头是最容易踩的 AI 味雷区。\n\n## 写作习惯\n\n- 写之前先判断:有没有独家take? 有→评论路径(短、锐、一个核心论点); 没有→报道路径或先不写。\n- 星际写文章前习惯先做竞品扫描,看最近3个月同话题别人怎么写的。\n- 偏好从具体经历和数据里长出观点,不是先摆观点再找例子。\n- 商单文章也要有自己的角度,不能写成软文模板。\n- 每篇文章约10处加粗标记重点,方便读者扫读。\n- 配图优先AI生成,HTML截图只在精确数据表格时兜底。\n\n## 技术偏好\n\n- 写代码优先TypeScript,除非明确要求JavaScript。\n\nSource: MEMORY.md#L1-L26","source":"memory","citation":"MEMORY.md#L1-L26","corpus":"memory"}],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":1110,"hits":1}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777221197537}}
{"type":"message","id":"1799f2ea","parentId":"0e7cdbbf","timestamp":"2026-04-26T16:33:24.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User asks: \"你的长期记忆中有些什么？\" They want to know what's in the long-term memory. We have MEMORY.md content. We should provide summary of key sections. Provide concise answer, following style rules: brief, direct, no filler, no AI voice. Should include maybe citation style? Not required but can reference. Provide bullet points? Avoid over-dividing. Keep to 1-3 sentences maybe plus brief list. The style: concise, direct, quick. Should answer."},{"type":"text","text":"长期记忆主要记录了你的**交流、写作、技术偏好以及工作方式**，概括如下：\n\n- **交流风格**：不喜欢标准助理腔、报告腔或套话；倾向先给判断再解释，若不确定直接说“我还在想”。  \n- **写作习惯**：写前先判断是否有独家视角（核心论点），需做竞品扫描，文章中约10处加粗重点，配图优先AI生成，实数据表格才用截图。  \n- **技术偏好**：代码首选 TypeScript，API 密钥走 `.env`，iOS 开发为主；不使用“退化”之类表述。  \n- **工作方式**：数据类任务要提炼结论并给出下一步建议，长任务需每2 分钟同步进展。  \n\n（摘自 `MEMORY.md`）"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"gpt-oss:120b-cloud","usage":{"input":19454,"output":315,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19769,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777221204296}}
